{{Documentation subpage}} <!-- PLEASE ADD CATEGORIES AND INTERWIKIS AT THE BOTTOM OF THIS PAGE. --> ==Usage== The template name is ''Facebook User'' and the first argument is the name of the Facebook account. This can be found in the page's [[Uniform Resource Locator|URL]]: if the URL is <tt><nowiki>http://www.facebooke.com/example</nowiki></tt>, the account name is ''example''.
== Examples == In this example, the Facebook user account is ''markzuckerberg'' and the description in the link is ''Mark Zuckerberg'' <nowiki>{{Facebook User|markzuckerberg|Mark Zuckerberg}}</nowiki> {{Facebook User|markzuckerberg|Mark Zuckerberg}}
In this example, the Facebook user account is ''8857543'' and the description in the link is ''Jennifer Aniston'' <nowiki>{{Facebook User|profile.php?id=68310606562|Mark Zuckerberg}}</nowiki> {{Facebook User|profile.php?id=68310606562|Mark Zuckerberg}}
