==Usage== {{See also|Wikipedia:External links/Perennial websites}}
The first parameter for the {{tl|Facebook}} template is the name of the Facebook account. This can be found in the page's [[Uniform Resource Locator|URL]]. For example: if the URL is <tt><nowiki>http://www.facebook.com/example</nowiki></tt>, then the account name is ''example''. The second parameter is the description or display name.
