            "required": false
        }
    }
}
</templatedata>

== Tracking category ==
* {{clc|Facebook ID different from Wikidata}} – ''comparison is [[:en:Case insensitive|Case insensitive]], so [https://www.facebook.com/zuck zuck] matches [https://www.facebook.com/Zuck Zuck]''
* {{clc|Facebook ID not in Wikidata}}
* {{clc|Facebook template missing ID and not in Wikidata}}
* {{clc|Pages using Facebook with unknown parameters}}

